Attributes are the basic building blocks of a creature; they determine their overall ability and competence in almost all aspects of the game.
A "0" score is average for a person of average health, experience, education and training.
A "+5" score is the pinnacle of achievement, beyond this is impossible to achieve naturally.
A "-5" is an often-fatal disability/deficit, and represents a total lack of ability.
A "-3" represents a severe deficit or defect that prevents or at least hinders normal life.
